    "name": "时空重构",
    "steam_appid": 3292340,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292340/extras/f4f9010f93b6de3b4e06dd9cbecd7ed3.avif?t=1748424381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292340/extras_big/f4f9010f93b6de3b4e06dd9cbecd7ed3.avif?t=1748424381 width=800 height=337 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果明天就是世界末日，那你最想去做些什么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是抛下一切去拯救世界？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还是选择与自己的爱人，共度这最后的时刻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292340/extras/38970b483dadad6e428726ac2186ae2a.avif?t=1748424381\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>端庄明艳的青梅竹马</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“我会一直陪着你的，过去是这样，未来也一定会是这样。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292340/extras/ddf987093d1094619f33042629e9616a.avif?t=1748424381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292340/extras_big/ddf987093d1094619f33042629e9616a.avif?t=1748424381 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>飒爽果决的性感特工</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“或许你还没有搞清楚状况，信仰、使命、情感？那些只是拖累生存的幻想。在我们的世界里，只有成为能一直掌控局面的人，才能活下去。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292340/extras/4190529fbda5e1218dfd0e10d88af6a5.avif?t=1748424381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292340/extras_big/4190529fbda5e1218dfd0e10d88af6a5.avif?t=1748424381 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>懵懂但博学的神秘少女</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“你是我漫长生命中唯一的光点，是我与这个世界唯一的连接。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292340/extras/a6a4616a6a398bf65df4b243426e358b.avif?t=1748424381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292340/extras_big/a6a4616a6a398bf65df4b243426e358b.avif?t=1748424381 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>温婉知性的贴身女仆</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“想哭就要哭出来啊，别害怕，我还在呢。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292340/extras/b9709ec802d595009cca2863a89ee55e.avif?t=1748424381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292340/extras_big/b9709ec802d595009cca2863a89ee55e.avif?t=1748424381 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>天真烂漫的名门少女</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“带上我，一起逃跑吧！”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292340/extras/5326a58b8659bf68663769d16dbcc4c7.avif?t=1748424381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292340/extras_big/5326a58b8659bf68663769d16dbcc4c7.avif?t=1748424381 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你喜欢的是危险又美丽的坏女人，那我们还有……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“就让你和我停留在这一刻吧，过了今晚，就不要再记得我了。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>更多可探索的内容</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数百条分支，几十个结局，你的每个决定都影响着角色的命运，任何选择都有可能将事件带往新的方向。每个玩家的游戏流程都会是独一无二的，同时游戏还提供了丰富的隐藏内容供玩家进行探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>全新的冒险故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >架空世界观的故事背景，给了作品更大的舞台与想象空间，能让玩家从更多维度去谱写独属于自己的史诗故事；除了爱情之外，你还将获得一段波澜壮阔，紧张刺激的冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多元的游戏体验</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独具匠心的诚意之作，被打磨的不止有“选择”。我们为你准备了更为丰富的交互内容，探索、战斗、收集，作品将用极致的“爽感”与“沉浸体验”，回应你的每一个行动，游戏不息，惊喜不断。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>极致的视觉享受</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >五名风格迥异的女主伴你游玩——或冷艳、或端庄、或可爱、或浪漫，亦或柔情似水，性感妩媚。多个时代，不同国度的美女等你来攻略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>关注我们</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎关注我们了解《时空重构》的最新进展：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方QQ①群：2150302479</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方QQ②群：632140116</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方QQ③群：939148359</p>",
